readable.content: A person in a field walks toward their white and orange parachute while another holds it . People collecting a parachute after landing on the ground . The parachutist is standing in a field near to his unfurled parachute . Two people fold a parachute after they have landed in a field . Two people on a grassy plain are gathering a parachute that one of the people just used .
